 Naomi Campbell is a new yummy mummy! The model took to her Instagram handle to share a cute photo, announcing the arrival of her baby girl, with the caption: “A beautiful little blessing has chosen me to be her mother, so honored to have this gentle soul in my life. There are no words to describe the lifelong bond that I now share with you my angel. There is no greater love.” View this post on Instagram A post shared by Naomi Campbell (@naomi) It is unclear who the father is and whether Campbell gave birth, hired a surrogate or adopted the little one.